{"tid":492285,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"酒店大整蠱 女廁裝透明玻璃益樓下途人","createTime":"2017-12-07T11:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T04:06:17.000Z","uid":33072,"like":95,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"eba207666d0be353e8472943c2c047bcd1899a06","tid":492285,"uid":33072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T11:32:13.000Z","msg":"外國人真係唔同啲，思想特別開放？時下好多建築都講求空間感，風格都偏向用自然光加上透明玻璃，明白嘅！喂，但係連廁所都要咁設計，會唔會有點兒哪個？美國媒體披露，一間酒店嘅新裝修，竟然重新設計女廁，全部外牆用上透明玻璃，仲要係對正廁格，基本上由入廁所開始一刻已經全程畀樓下途人直擊，而女廁亦無任何百頁窗遮掩。但估唔到，好多女人竟然唔介意，如常照用廁所，而且毫無遮掩。不過有人抨擊酒店做法有搏出位之嫌，而且連一啲警告字眼都無，可以話係「出賣」酒店用戶；途人亦爭相駐足觀望，仲有唔少人舉機影相，實屬不雅！小編即刻諗起之前中國都有酒店採用360度全透明玻璃設計，不過廁所係位於一間深山入面嘅酒店，所以係等用家觀景周圍大自然；而唔係畀周圍嘅人觀賞用家囉，啋！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PCx.SVXm_U4i9LZMDKi_WA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTUwO2g9MzM3O2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com/64c80d85346fef43197ac1d7a87d5fbc/tumblr_inline_p0jphrU0Gt1t92yk3_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPCx.SVXm_U4i9LZMDKi_WA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTUwO2g9MzM3O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F64c80d85346fef43197ac1d7a87d5fbc%2Ftumblr_inline_p0jphrU0Gt1t92yk3_1280.jpg&h=ce55dc7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Z4s8VCnnkwMc0EMrhn9HzQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTUwO2g9MzIyO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com/0f272548128508809ce99a6add4fc0bf/tumblr_inline_p0jphsq58d1t92yk3_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZ4s8VCnnkwMc0EMrhn9HzQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTUwO2g9MzIyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F0f272548128508809ce99a6add4fc0bf%2Ftumblr_inline_p0jphsq58d1t92yk3_1280.jpg&h=f1052d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NeTk4xk_Mk18Z3ITjwcEmA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTUwO2g9MzE2O2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com